<h3><a href="https://docs.wpilib.org/en/stable/docs/software/telemetry/writing-sendable-classes.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow ugc">Writing Your Own Sendable Classes</a></h3>

  <p>Since the Sendable interface only has one method, writing your own classes that implement Sendable(and thus automatically log values to and/or consume values from the dashboard) is extremely easy: ...</p>


